-- Silver Standard to Sell Snowfield, Brucejack to Pretium for $450 Million
-- B y   T o n y   B a r r e t t
-- 2010-10-29T09:10:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-29/silver-standard-to-sell-snowfield-brucejack-to-pretium-for-450-million.html
Silver Standard Resources Inc. said
it has agreed to sell its Snowfield and Brucejack Projects in
northern British Columbia to Pretium Resources Inc. for a total
of $450 million. It commented in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tony Barrett at 
 tbarrett4@bloomberg.net  